    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">An indication of the different capabilities of the various versions of MODFLOW can be found in </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Input_files_Supported_in_Vario" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Input Files Supported in Various Versions of MODFLOW</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></para>
